WEBVTT

00:05:30.008 --> 00:05:32.333
But, in recent years,

00:05:32.357 --> 00:05:34.281
at the time of this conversation,

00:05:34.305 --> 00:05:37.535
they had nothing
but long periods of drought,

00:05:37.559 --> 00:05:39.210
and then flash flooding,

00:05:39.234 --> 00:05:40.955
and then more drought.

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:42.821
The school had been destroyed,

00:05:42.845 --> 00:05:44.384
livelihoods had been destroyed,

00:05:44.408 --> 00:05:46.182
their harvest had been destroyed.

00:05:46.206 --> 00:05:50.812
She forms this women's group
to try to keep her community together.

00:05:51.169 --> 00:05:56.329
And this was a reality
that really struck me,

00:05:56.353 --> 00:06:00.738
because of course,
